<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
</head>
<body>
  <b>Hi there! Wordsmith is a tool designed to help you study. If you have a webpage full of terms you need to learn, Wordsmith with gather them all into a collection, let you edit their definitions, and help you study.</b>

  <div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span6">
      <h2>Word Sets</h2>
      <ul>
        <% @wordsets.each do |wordset| %>
          <li><%= link_to wordset.name, wordset %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <h2>Create A New Wordset!</h2>
        <p>Pop in the URL from which to generate your new wordset:</p>
        <%= render "form" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

